    "### The E-Commerce Profitability\n",
    "Identifying High-Value Categories and Seasonal Revenue \n",
    "\n",
    "1. **About dataset and Understanding business model**:\n",
    "    The company industry we analyse below is e-commerce marketplace sector, so their revenue received through Commission fee on sales of the Seller. \n",
    "\n",
    "2. **Business Assumption**:\n",
    "    The dataset does not include Commission revenue, so i assume the Commission fee would be 30% of the order price.\n",
    "\n",
    "3. **Business Problems**:\n",
    "    Which 20% of product categories generate 80% of the revenue (Pareto Principle)?\n",
    "    How do delivery times in different Brazilian states correlate with customer review scores (and thus, future retention)?\n",
    "4. Methodology and skills:\n",
    "    Python (Cleaning/EDA) + SQL (Aggregation) + Power BI (Basic Trend Lines).\n"
   ]
